            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Sexti Marciani diamysus ad <lb n="2"/>veteres cicatrices <expan><abbr>compl</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Sexti Marciani t<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>alas</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="2"/>eros <expan><abbr>delacrimatori</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucii</ex></expan> Sexti Marciani dialepidos <lb n="2"/>ad aspritudinem tol<expan><ex>l</ex><abbr>e</abbr><ex>ndam</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Sexti Marciani diasmyr<lb break="no" n="2"/>nes post impetum <expan><abbr>lippi</abbr><ex>tudines</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Augenarztstempel. Die Inschrift befindet sich auf den vier Seiten. (B): (o. Autor): Text 2; Z. 1: t(h)alass/eros.</p>
